data.text:
Meet your new competitive Edge - The Varsity Edge Cheer Shoes. Compromise nothing with two pairs of insoles: the TECH fit is engineered for strike support and the COMFORT fit is engineered for arch support. A classic, lightweight body and an athletic attitude gives these premium cheer shoes unyielding flexibility, durability, and breath-ability for a performance grade experience. Welcome to the future of cheer footwear.

Choose Your Fit:

1. The TECH fit: comes with striking (to rebound and accelerate) and dampening (absorption) gel pads in the forefoot and heel - all centered around solid arch support.

2. The COMFORT fit: luxury memory foam arch support geared towards comfort.

This white shoe is available in Adult and Youth sizes.

VE17/VE17Y
